HEADWORD: Heartquake
<hw>Heart"quake`</hw> <pr>(-kw⟦amac⟧k`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<def>Trembling of the heart; trepidation; fear.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>In many an hour of danger and <qex>heartquake</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Hawthorne.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Heartrending</ent>⟦br⟧
